    "(iii) How to reduce uncertainties about the eventual host plant species in the landscape that were carrying the pathogens detected in the sentinel insects?",
    "The answers to these questions are obviously dependent on the specific environment and trophic chains at stake, and necessitate further multidisciplinary research.",
